---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Test Automation">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-cogs"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Smart Automation Strategy at the Right Time</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies collaborates with clients to understand their requirements and business before suggesting an automation strategy implemented at exactly the right stages of the development process — using proprietary Test Labs backed by industry-specific open-source frameworks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-desktop"></i></div>
            <h5>UI Automation</h5>
            <p>Selenium, RFT, TestComplete, SilkTest, QuickTest Pro and Auto IT for comprehensive graphical user interface automation testing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-search-plus"></i></div>
            <h5>Code Scanning</h5>
            <p>Static analysis using PMD, FxCop, PREfast, PREfix and PREsharp to catch defects and code quality issues before runtime.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-plug"></i></div>
            <h5>API Test Automation</h5>
            <p>JUnit and NUnit frameworks for automated API and integration testing, ensuring all service contracts behave as expected.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-pie-chart"></i></div>
            <h5>Code Coverage</h5>
            <p>Clover, Ncover, EMMA and Bullseye for accurate code coverage measurement, ensuring every code path is exercised.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-flask"></i></div>
            <h5>Test Labs</h5>
            <p>In-house Test Labs housing proprietary frameworks and industry-specific open-source tools built around automation objectives.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-certificate"></i></div>
            <h5>Certified Experts</h5>
            <p>Certified automation specialists adopting a consulting approach that reduces risk and maximises return on investment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
